{"tid":2350289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大紀元都搞經濟圈，希望成功","createTime":"2021-01-02T07:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T13:25:19.000Z","uid":171506,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"464e3dcb37284ba7c7a6cdb86d8f1fbc5921e927","tid":2350289,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfhQedF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfhQedF.jpg&h=c7959478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"830b47f470c6b0e34f3dee2575925c7b583ca433","tid":2350289,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"86189dc64bac1cef6079acad8a9e650a84d28972","tid":2350289,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"830b47f470c6b0e34f3dee2575925c7b583ca433","tid":2350289,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"2718696c5fd405b6e8b4dc0cc4b0d60eb59ed8a3","tid":2350289,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"大紀元已經喺世界身價暴漲：<br />\n<br />\n英文版大紀元奪美國本月app store 第一媒體類下載量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[突發]美國總統轉載大紀元新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308034</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連美國總統都有份宣傳，宜家Trump 七千萬支持者爭住下載英文大紀元app<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3dKjrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3dKjrL.jpg&h=453fac5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YyaZrM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YyaZrM.jpg&h=073af4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMiBUZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMiBUZ7.jpg&h=2c2b76bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，大紀元的確係講緊真話，可能有三成誇大但整體事實都係真嘅，袁弓夷都成日都喺佢地度講嘢，但仍然有唔少五毛刻意宣傳大紀元係fake news，最緊要我都覺得係要批判性思考，唔好比軸心國嘅概念同文化入侵大家嘅思想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nvyNJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nvyNJq.jpg&h=6bf32f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現中共有兩個招數去對付反共媒體<br />\n<br />\n第一種係洗腦式抹黑，好似大紀元咁因為唔係起源於香港本土，所以大眾起初唔知係咩來頭，中共馬上開動宣傳機器，<span class=\"gold\">直接向公眾渲染法輪功同旗下嘅大紀元為邪教，令大家一見法輪功同大紀元即刻避之則吉，驚佢傳教</span>，中共成功洗腦令大家一開始就先入為主覺得法輪功同大紀元係邪教，從而減少公眾接觸到大紀元資訊嘅機會同動機<br />\n<br />\n第二種係分化，好似蘋果日報咁由於九七回歸前已紮根香港一段時間，大眾普遍對蘋果日報有一定認識，中共難以進行抹黑，於是唯有不斷引導分化民主陣營唔同光譜嘅人，孤立蘋果日報地位（其實如果對蘋果日報有少少認識就知蘋果一直都係屬於上一個世紀以司徒華、李柱銘為首嘅傳統泛民光譜，對後來興起而又漸成主流嘅本土派嚟講，蘋果日報有少少愚鈍亦不足為奇，咁當然宜家睇返轉頭好多傳統泛民亦只係思想滯後嘅牛皮燈籠），分裂民主陣營，再將敵人逐一消滅"},{"pid":"10ecdca879ef200a094c5db0ed3a05d70e033365","tid":2350289,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"祝福佢"},{"pid":"e463d715c7ee6f1d27ad2ebfed25a4124588b93f","tid":2350289,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1336eb0f20044bb5b1ae25bdcfa0d8c6838cfeae","tid":2350289,"uid":183391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}